{
    "type": "script",
    "id": "d563997d-2e4b-4755-9a6e-e7d47ba2acff",
    "name": "Katie RR13_DeadNights",
    "sceneId": "84006d08-8e6d-4558-b9b5-101f3c3054fe",
    "actorId": "0b49e2c8-5b7f-4534-bd10-21a0a36a6cbe",
    "trigger": {
        "type": "triggers.manual",
        "name": "Manual"
    },
    "entryPoints": [
        {
            "type": "scripts.entryPoint",
            "id": "36725dad-9bd6-4b53-b278-0379ff5b38b8",
            "name": "Main",
            "nodes": [
                {
                    "type": "nodes.showMenu",
                    "id": "8c8732cb-e5da-4e03-9310-514cd7a8d61c",
                    "options": [
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "887ccb66-c9f2-4768-a05d-4f47c7b92325",
                            "text": "Talk About Katie",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "ed35df31-278d-4138-85fd-8aef361e7f0a",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "0b49e2c8-5b7f-4534-bd10-21a0a36a6cbe",
                                    "text": "How about you, Katie... aren't you bothered by all these ghosts?",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "c2f0a747-d926-4558-813f-4bc3f9898968",
                                    "actorId": "0b49e2c8-5b7f-4534-bd10-21a0a36a6cbe",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "As long as they aren't sliming my face with their tongues or licking the food off my plate, I have no problem with the ghosts around here.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "7df1d681-81e7-4821-bd66-fd9f29959755",
                                    "actorId": "0b49e2c8-5b7f-4534-bd10-21a0a36a6cbe",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "However, I wouldn't want to be out on the streets of Caligari right now. I've heard a lot of rumors of people who were scared to death on the Nights of the Dead.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "5",
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "7d2a8402-7051-4c75-8ba2-45ea132a3135",
                            "text": "Talk About Ghosts",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "74a06089-68ec-4468-a550-3c21a2f85c03",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "0b49e2c8-5b7f-4534-bd10-21a0a36a6cbe",
                                    "text": "You said something about ghosts at your inn?",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "5f173e63-4de6-420b-8a09-09a5d84292c6",
                                    "actorId": "0b49e2c8-5b7f-4534-bd10-21a0a36a6cbe",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Our inn has been around for decades long before my parents took it over. On the Nights of the Dead, a couple of ghost sailors would show up and always sit at a table by the fire.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "ba9b370a-605f-4967-b926-4bb23c9acc48",
                                    "actorId": "0b49e2c8-5b7f-4534-bd10-21a0a36a6cbe",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "I never knew who they were - they must have died a long time ago. Still, they always seemed so friendly and happy to be at the inn that as a child I thought of them as my long-lost friends.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "f41b584f-b687-4965-b13e-08bdf7cff499",
                                    "actorId": "0b49e2c8-5b7f-4534-bd10-21a0a36a6cbe",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "I guess that just goes to show why I'm not particularly frightened by Undead pirates. On the whole, though, I prefer ghosts to zombies... ghosts don't smell so bad.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "7",
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "780a619f-c525-4b1c-8911-04bdbe384b75",
                            "text": "Flirt With Katie",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                    "id": "8a089f16-ad35-469f-abd1-294a81a33d10",
                                    "actorId": "0b49e2c8-5b7f-4534-bd10-21a0a36a6cbe",
                                    "amount": "1",
                                    "change": "1",
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "e98d4629-4602-407f-9837-d9a4a2c425d4",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "0b49e2c8-5b7f-4534-bd10-21a0a36a6cbe",
                                    "text": "I'll be happy to escort you back to your room and make sure that no ghosts try to kiss you.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "4a11eb00-ca6e-4f9f-8160-0e1f2f95b28d",
                                    "actorId": "0b49e2c8-5b7f-4534-bd10-21a0a36a6cbe",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "In that case, it's not the ghosts who want to kiss me that I'd have to watch out for...",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "3",
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "a9707b19-ae7a-43af-b3bd-33d83da9059d",
                            "text": "Say Goodnight",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "ca4802de-77ce-4380-9aae-6cacf4bd9328",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "0b49e2c8-5b7f-4534-bd10-21a0a36a6cbe",
                                    "text": "Good night, sleep tight, don't let the ghosts give you a fright!",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "a6716987-550f-4ef6-9453-4a15830acd8a",
                                    "actorId": "0b49e2c8-5b7f-4534-bd10-21a0a36a6cbe",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Yeah, sure... goodnight, Shawn.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": true,
                            "minutes": "2",
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        }
                    ],
                    "AutoAddDone": false,
                    "Unique": false
                }
            ]
        }
    ]
}